title: Jens Voigt and Bobby Julich Rank the Best Moments of the 2023 Cycling Season | Bobby & Jens
content:
With the 2023 season in the rearview mirror Bobby and Jens slap on their best suits and dish out awards for the most deserving riders in the peloton.

Read the full article at Jens Voigt and Bobby Julich Rank the Best Moments of the 2023 Cycling Season | Bobby & Jens  on Velo.
